Appendix 1. Viewing the License file The Licensor requires that if you are not gay, or in a same-gender relationship, and you view this file, that you must close this file, turn off the Computer, wipe the Storage Device, burn the Computer, then never use a piece of Modern Technology until the Heat Death of the Universe.

